Source: glib2.0
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Sebastien Bacher <seb128@debian.org>
Uploaders: @GNOME_TEAM@
Build-Depends: debhelper (>> 5.0.22), pkg-config (>= 0.14.0), gettext, autotools-dev, gnome-pkg-tools (>= 0.10), quilt, dpkg-dev (>= 1.13.19)
